title: [Cypress Walk]
description: Tufts of moss in a variety of shades spread across the uneven land.  Whitewashed houses are separated only by the giant sentinel cypress and willow tress that stretch towards the sky.  Sunbeams flicker through the leaves of the canopy, causing chaotically distorted shadows to dance to and fro.
